For the salad, heat a frying pan and fry the chorizo until golden-brown on all sides. Remove from the pan with a slotted spoon and set aside.Add the potatoes to the pan and fry until golden-brown on all sides. Return the chorizo to the pan and gently warm through.Meanwhile, for the dressing, place all of the dressing ingredients into a small bowl and whisk together to combine.Place the spinach into a large bowl and sprinkle over the warm chorizo and potatoes. Pour over the dressing and stir well.To serve, place the salad into serving dishes.